edu.lehigh.cse.lol

Class Goodie

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.lehigh.cse.lol.PhysicsSprite
      • edu.lehigh.cse.lol.Goodie

  • public class Goodie
extends PhysicsSprite
    Goodies are physical entities in a game whose main purpose is for the hero to collect them. Collecting a goodie has three possible consequences: it can lead to the score changing, it can lead to the hero's strength changing, and it can lead to the hero becoming invincible for some time.
